      "version": 352,
      "versionNonce": 179793491,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783454632603,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "\"Aspire\"\n    - A better \"docker compose'\n    - let's you create an environment, manage it,\n      collect and view OTEL data, etc.\n    - It's really good at all that.\n    - It is not .NET specific\n        - I' use it with node, go, Java\n    - The other side: You can have it \"deploy\" your software.\n        - we are not going to do this.\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\"Aspire\"\n    - A better \"docker compose'\n    - let's you create an environment, manage it,\n      collect and view OTEL data, etc.\n    - It's really good at all that.\n    - It is not .NET specific\n        - I' use it with node, go, Java\n    - The other side: You can have it \"deploy\" your software.\n        - we are not going to do this.\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    }
